<br>
First attempt using Velium Recurve Bow and 3dmg summoned arrows - Scored a 511 crit, and highest non-crit was 298.<br>
<br>
Second attempt using the same bow and 10dmg shadow-tipped arrows - Scored zero crits, and highest non crit was 283.<br>
<br>
It appears that I did more damage using a lower damage arrow. If anyone knows why this could be, please post here. <p><center>Ginweil Splitfeather
57 Outrider - Infinitus Vindicat<BR>
